32:36.600 --> 32:38.420
I got a lot of things--I'm
thinking about life

32:38.540 --> 32:40.428
and--and time.
Sarah: Yeah. I know.

32:40.540 --> 32:42.360
Hank: And--and--and--you know--
Sarah: It's being in

32:42.470 --> 32:44.609
this whole place.
