32:44.720 --> 32:47.780
Hank: Not being afraid though...
Sarah: Count your blessings.

32:47.890 --> 32:49.448
Yeah.
Hank: Doing the right thing--

32:49.550 --> 32:51.586
Sarah: Ifeel like.
Hank: What's good for yourself--

32:51.690 --> 32:53.783
Sarah: Iagree.
Hank: Not being afraid, and--

32:53.900 --> 32:56.061
Sarah: No, that's why we should
probably be vegetarians.

32:56.180 --> 32:57.966
Hank: We should get married,
Sarah.

32:58.070 --> 33:03.098
We should get married.
Yeah.

33:07.220 --> 33:10.940
Sarah: Oh...Hank.

33:11.050 --> 33:14.019
Hank: I--I love you.
And--and--and--

33:14.130 --> 33:17.156
I wanna marry you and--

33:17.270 --> 33:20.785
I want to. I don't wanna be
