33:20.890 --> 33:23.404
I just want to, uh...

33:27.280 --> 33:31.899
I wanna be all in.

33:32.010 --> 33:34.171
You know, you know...

33:34.280 --> 33:37.249
Sarah: I'm just so, um,
surprised.

33:37.360 --> 33:40.045
Hank: Yeah. Yeah, yeah, yeah,
yeah. I don't know why

33:40.150 --> 33:43.665
I--I can always say things in
weird times, but...

33:43.780 --> 33:48.774
You don't have to...you wanna
bring them the cookies?

33:48.880 --> 33:50.700
We don't--we don't have to--

33:50.820 --> 33:54.199
Sarah: No, Ijust--
Hank: I mean, if it's a no...

33:54.300 --> 33:59.920
Then, uh, you know...

34:00.030 --> 34:02.965
Is it a no?

34:03.070 --> 34:06.176
Sarah: Let's--let's talk later.

34:06.280 --> 34:07.827
Hank: All right.

34:07.940 --> 34:10.864
We'll talk about it then.

34:10.970 --> 34:13.859
At a better time.
Sarah: Yes. Thank you.

34:13.980 --> 34:15.902
That would be great.
Hank: Yeah?

34:16.010 --> 34:18.114
Sarah: Yeah.
Hank: All right.

34:18.220 --> 34:20.154
Sarah: Okay.

34:21.950 --> 34:24.259
Hank: All right.
Sarah: Okay.

34:31.690 --> 34:33.920
Hank: Hey. I just proposed.
