34:34.030 --> 34:35.372
nurse: Oh, well,
congratulations.

34:35.480 --> 34:37.471
Hank: Yeah...yeah, well,
thank you.

34:37.590 --> 34:40.753
We're gonna talk about it.
We're gonna talk about it.

34:40.870 --> 34:42.098
It's like a maybe.

