35:00.200 --> 35:02.259
Zeek: Ah, Millie.

35:02.370 --> 35:05.544
It's a terrible thing to put you
through.

35:05.650 --> 35:07.470
I'm so sorry I scared you
like that.

35:07.580 --> 35:11.095
Camille: Yeah. It was about as
scared as I've ever been.

35:11.210 --> 35:13.417
Zeek: Yeah.

35:13.520 --> 35:16.068
I mean, my God, Millie.

35:16.180 --> 35:18.831
How the hell
did we end up here?

35:21.360 --> 35:23.874
I mean, don't you wish we'd just
go back a couple years?

35:23.980 --> 35:28.349
Just, you know, you and me
that--

35:28.470 --> 35:32.429
have some fun, you know?

35:32.540 --> 35:37.534
Camille: We'll do it again.

35:37.650 --> 35:40.813
Zeek: I'm _not sure about this
operation thing, MIllIe.

35:40.930 --> 35:42.545
Camille: Well, we don't have to
