35:45.100 --> 35:47.546
We'll talk about it, we'll
decide, we'll talk to the kids--

35:47.660 --> 35:54.316
Zeek: No. No I don't want the
kids involved in this.

35:54.420 --> 35:59.426
We'll make the decision,
you and me.

36:04.610 --> 36:07.431
Camille: [choking up] Okay.
