36:12.610 --> 36:14.646
Camille: Oh.
Zeek: Oh, hey, guys.

36:17.070 --> 36:20.540
Hi. Hi, Amber.
Amber: Hi.

36:20.660 --> 36:22.480
Zeek: Hi, honey.
Amber: Hey, is this okay?

36:22.590 --> 36:25.627
Zeek: Yeah. Hi, sweetheart.

36:28.730 --> 36:32.837
How are you?
You feeling all right?

36:32.940 --> 36:35.568
Oh, my gosh.
[Amber chuckles]

36:35.670 --> 36:37.183
Amber: How you doing?
You all right?

36:37.290 --> 36:40.635
Zeek: Yeah. Yeah, I feel like
a million bucks.

36:40.750 --> 36:44.151
Amber: You look great.
