36:44.270 --> 36:47.057
Zeek: Hey, come here. Hi.
Drew: Grandpa.

36:47.170 --> 36:49.479
Zeek: Grandson.

36:49.580 --> 36:52.515
Drew: I love you, Grandpa.

36:52.620 --> 36:54.827
Zeek: I love you too, kid.

36:56.930 --> 36:58.306
Joel: Well, I don't know,

36:58.420 --> 37:01.344
I guess outside of a hospital
is romantic.

37:01.460 --> 37:02.347
Hank: Yeah.
Joel: In a way.

37:02.460 --> 37:04.075
Hank: It's a little weird, yeah.

37:04.180 --> 37:07.661
Well, you know, even--even when
