37:17.230 --> 37:19.266
Joel: And she didn't say no.

37:19.370 --> 37:20.439
Hank: Not yet.

37:20.540 --> 37:22.599
Joel: That's big.
Hank: Yeah.

37:22.720 --> 37:23.402
We'll see.

37:23.510 --> 37:24.886
Joel: Good luck to us.

37:25.000 --> 37:27.059
Hank: Yeah, man.

37:27.170 --> 37:29.161
Cheers to that.

37:29.280 --> 37:30.656
Crosby: Worst day ever.

