know what your dream car is.

38:05.900 --> 38:08.824
Adam: Uh...I like that
Porsche Cayenne.

38:08.940 --> 38:09.861
Hybnd.

38:09.970 --> 38:11.551
[Crosby laughs]

38:11.660 --> 38:12.763
What?

38:12.870 --> 38:14.485
It's practical. You put the
family in there.

38:14.600 --> 38:17.251
It's easy on the environment,
but it's a Porsche.

38:17.360 --> 38:18.384
Crosby: You're right that
it's practical.

38:18.500 --> 38:20.218
It's practically not a Porsche.

38:20.330 --> 38:22.298
But, regardless, fine,
you're in a Cayenne.

38:22.400 --> 38:25.119
Adam: Porsche Cayenne.
Crosby: I'm in a Lambo.

38:25.230 --> 38:28.438
The point is...

38:28.540 --> 38:30.576
I've thought it over and I don't
want to cash out

38:30.680 --> 38:32.853
with this insurance money.

38:32.960 --> 38:35.064
I don't think that's right.
I think, you know,

38:35.170 --> 38:37.786
when we started that company we
were at zero and we took it

38:37.900 --> 38:40.232
somewhere amazing and now we're
not at zero.

38:40.350 --> 38:42.580
I mean, yeah, we've had our legs
taken out, but

38:42.690 --> 38:48.105
between you and I--I just--
I would bet on us.

38:48.220 --> 38:51.075
And I don't think we should let
one rough year break us.

38:51.190 --> 38:53.078
That's not who we are.

38:53.190 --> 38:56.045
We're partners, right?

38:56.160 --> 38:57.673
Partners?

38:57.780 --> 39:00.840
Adam: Yeah. Yeah. Partners.

39:08.960 --> 39:10.541
Sarah: How are you doing?

39:10.650 --> 39:12.402
Amber: Oh, exhausted.
Sarah: Yeah?

39:12.520 --> 39:15.375
Amber: I just wanna go crawl
into bed and sleep

39:15.490 --> 39:16.889
for the next three weeks.

39:17.000 --> 39:20.697
Sarah: All right, well,
before you do that...

39:20.800 --> 39:23.177
I have something to show you.

39:23.290 --> 39:24.279
Amber: I don't like this.
[Sarah laughs]

39:24.390 --> 39:26.767
[overlapping chatter]

39:26.880 --> 39:30.668
Sarah: Here she is!
Amber: Oh, my God, what is this?

39:30.780 --> 39:32.498
Sarah: We couldn't get to the
shower so we brought the shower

39:32.610 --> 39:33.941
to you.
Amber: You didn't have

39:34.060 --> 39:35.630
to do this.

