Look at all these embarrassing
pictures of me.

39:37.370 --> 39:39.292
Sarah: I know!
Julia: There's so many.

39:39.410 --> 39:40.889
Sarah: And you have presents.

39:40.990 --> 39:42.548
Amber: Oh, guys, no...

39:42.650 --> 39:44.823
Kristina: Rounded what we could
from--

39:44.930 --> 39:47.205
both: From Pierre's.
[both laughing]

39:47.310 --> 39:49.687
Sarah: We brought all your
presents here and we have

39:49.800 --> 39:53.657
our treats and this book
which we made.

39:53.770 --> 39:56.238
It's a tradition that Mom
started and she made one

39:56.350 --> 39:57.738
for Julia and I.

39:57.840 --> 40:02.493
Each of the moms wrote a page
of advice for you.

40:02.600 --> 40:04.807
And then the rest of the book
IS empty.

40:04.910 --> 40:09.563
And you fill it up with--with
the new, uh, new guy.

40:09.680 --> 40:11.989
[laughter]
You start.

40:12.090 --> 40:14.194
Kristina: Okay. So I'm not sure
how this is going to sound,

40:14.300 --> 40:16.882
because I_was a half a bottle of
wme In. Not qUIte sure

40:17.000 --> 40:18.991
this is going to be--
Amber: That's the advice.

40:19.100 --> 40:20.442
Drink wine.

40:20.550 --> 40:21.892
Kristina: Okay, um...

40:22.000 --> 40:24.719
The thing I would say, Amber,
about motherhood

40:24.830 --> 40:29.244
is that you're going to get
curve balls thrown at you.

40:29.350 --> 40:30.999
A lot of curve balls.
And sometimes,

40:31.110 --> 40:35.114
they're gonna make you want to
run and hide, or despair...

40:35.220 --> 40:40.089
My wisdom for you is to embrace
those curve balls

40:40.190 --> 40:42.750
and own them.

40:42.850 --> 40:45.648
And I know in my heart that
you're gonna be the best mom in

40:45.750 --> 40:48.605
the whole world. Because you're
the best kid in the world.

40:48.720 --> 40:51.097
Julia: I know you're going to be
a wonderful mother.

40:51.200 --> 40:55.307
Because you're so smart
and funny and wise,

40:55.410 --> 40:58.106
and you have a huge heart.

40:58.210 --> 41:00.519
And I know you'll do right by
your child.

41:00.630 --> 41:03.895
But you also have to do right
by yourself.

41:04.010 --> 41:08.117
A huge part of being a mom
is--is being a good role model.

41:08.220 --> 41:09.869
So what I'll say to you is,

41:09.980 --> 41:12.631
don't ever give up on
your own dreams.

41:12.740 --> 41:14.605
And don't let anybody tell you
that you can't do it all,

41:14.710 --> 41:15.631
because we can.
Jasmine: I've always loved

41:15.740 --> 41:17.742
and admired what a proud person
you are.

41:17.850 --> 41:19.772
You're so independent
and strong.

41:19.890 --> 41:21.881
But I just want you to make sure
that you don't ever feel

41:21.990 --> 41:25.198
too proud to come to me
or your mom or any of us.

41:25.310 --> 41:27.619
Because we're here for you.

41:27.720 --> 41:30.473
And we wanna help you.
So don't ever hesitate to

41:30.590 --> 41:33.229
pick up the phone.

41:33.350 --> 41:36.478
[low chatter, laughter]

41:36.590 --> 41:38.694
Sarah: Amber...

41:43.390 --> 41:46.211
Forget it.
No matter what...

41:46.330 --> 41:50.187
I will always have your back.

41:52.470 --> 41:54.438
Amber: I know.

41:54.540 --> 41:59.989
Camille: Amber...
I would say to you

42:00.100 --> 42:03.922
that life is short.

42:04.030 --> 42:09.559
You cannot know how impossibly
fast it goes by.

42:09.660 --> 42:14.381
So...just enjoy this baby.

42:14.490 --> 42:17.869
Cherish this time.

42:17.980 --> 42:22.428
Cherish every minute of it.

42:22.540 --> 42:27.568
In my eyes

